title: Ki Kids Cocineros
description: Kio, Kia, Pekas, Kate and the rest of the Ki-Kids guide two utensils to the kitchen of a famed chef, who's set to prepare a regal dinner for a visiting king in this charming installment of the children's series, presented in Spanish and English. The program emphasizes good table manners and how to respect your guests during a dinner. The series is designed to help children aged 3 and up learn English as a second language.
